    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not pregnancy though, i'm definitely not pregnant lol. i'm just really stressed with work and i've been feeling super bloated lately, so i'm pretty sure it's just gas trapped in my gut or something. i really don't want to go to the er and wait for 6 hours just for them to tell me to take more fiber. if i just take a couple of codeine tablets now, will that help me sleep through it? i just need the pain to stop so i can rest.",
